<div class="answer-head">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730"
class="zm-item-link-avatar"
href="/people/kaiserwang730">
<img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/21cb65b48_s.jpg"
class="zm-list-avatar"
data-source="//pic1.zhimg.com/21cb65b48_s.jpg" />
</a>



<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="967">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$jiang-xu-wei-32" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/jiang-xu-wei-32" class="zg-link" title="姜旭伟">姜旭伟</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$aaa-ssss-88" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/aaa-ssss-88" class="zg-link" title="AAA Ssss">AAA Ssss</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$chen-a-zhu-43" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/chen-a-zhu-43" class="zg-link" title="陈阿宁">陈阿宁</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="4190611" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix"><p>青龙偃月刀上一次重见天日，是在1994年的北京市朝阳区，目击者是一个叫和平的中年妇女。</p><br><br><p>女警察：“我们来呀，是为了了解情况。”</p><br><p>和平：“我正有情况要向您二位回报。我瞅见凶器了，就凶手使的那把刀。”</p><br><p>“差不多得……啊……这么长吧。”</p><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/423dafab2a655ea755a5420794e43a9b_b.jpg" data-rawheight="221" data-rawwidth="300" class="content_image" width="300"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawheight="221" data-rawwidth="300" class="content_image lazy" width="300" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/423dafab2a655ea755a5420794e43a9b_b.jpg"><br><p>“这么宽吧。”</p><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/be6d9c082c22b88ff106054a7ea34602_b.jpg" data-rawheight="218" data-rawwidth="300" class="content_image" width="300"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawheight="218" data-rawwidth="300" class="content_image lazy" width="300" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/be6d9c082c22b88ff106054a7ea34602_b.jpg"><br><p>男警察：“不是，大姐，您说的那可是青龙偃月刀，那是三国里面关云长使的。”</p><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/7ae380c4b81ef67a7476b8b12b82aa24_b.jpg" data-rawheight="221" data-rawwidth="300" class="content_image" width="300"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawheight="221" data-rawwidth="300" class="content_image lazy" width="300" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/7ae380c4b81ef67a7476b8b12b82aa24_b.jpg"><br><br><p>可惜的是，罗贯中和梁左都已经不在人世，所以青龙偃月刀现在的下落又成了谜团。</p><p>20年过去了，只有朝阳区的群众还在战斗着。</p><br><p>（我现在已经分不清“和平”和“知乎”了。）</p><br><br><p>——————————互动·更新——————————</p><br><p>1. 经热心乎友提醒，《我爱我家》的设定里的“家”在东城区，拍摄地点在西城区。</p><p>因为对朝阳区群众过于敬畏，我错想成朝阳区了。</p><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/78d38c9a722db716bc58c8dcf4e39db2_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="669" data-rawheight="92" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="669" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/78d38c9a722db716bc58c8dcf4e39db2_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="669" data-rawheight="92" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="669" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/78d38c9a722db716bc58c8dcf4e39db2_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/78d38c9a722db716bc58c8dcf4e39db2_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/95b184998a55d078842423f69c53dc3d_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="536" data-rawheight="73" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="536" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/95b184998a55d078842423f69c53dc3d_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="536" data-rawheight="73" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="536" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/95b184998a55d078842423f69c53dc3d_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/95b184998a55d078842423f69c53dc3d_b.jpg"><br>2. “和平”是直的，“知乎”是弯的。我现在能分清了。<noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/fe141cd3de09f14988c8d38d6aa737a7_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="671" data-rawheight="90" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="671" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/fe141cd3de09f14988c8d38d6aa737a7_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="671" data-rawheight="90" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="671" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/fe141cd3de09f14988c8d38d6aa737a7_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/fe141cd3de09f14988c8d38d6aa737a7_b.jpg"><br><p>3. 另有平友说，虽然罗贯中和梁左都已不在，但是我可以直接找知乎女士。</p><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/6f951f9463718b4087ab4ba5bb5a33f1_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="666" data-rawheight="91" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="666" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/6f951f9463718b4087ab4ba5bb5a33f1_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="666" data-rawheight="91" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="666" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/6f951f9463718b4087ab4ba5bb5a33f1_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/6f951f9463718b4087ab4ba5bb5a33f1_b.jpg"><br><p>后来我终于找到了和平女士，却不知该如何开口。</p><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/e3b0f955ffaa41193babb8dcd930a6fa_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="350" data-rawheight="521" class="content_image" width="350"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="350" data-rawheight="521" class="content_image lazy" width="350" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/e3b0f955ffaa41193babb8dcd930a6fa_b.jpg">


</div>

